  "3056570": {
    "name": "Deck of Memories",
    "steam_appid": 3056570,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《记忆卡牌》是一款卡牌养成类游戏，玩家将通过身临其境的卡牌全景透视图，深入了解最后一位灯塔看守人的生活。利用独特的卡牌制作机制定制自己的卡组，探索破碎的记忆碎片，揭开灯塔的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/fba9f169dddb8a0cf5fec28b4b9aafa8.avif?t=1770822592\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras_big/fba9f169dddb8a0cf5fec28b4b9aafa8.avif?t=1770822592 width=800 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/8f8db0bc275c751695175cdd63ca32e0.poster.avif?t=1770822592\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/8f8db0bc275c751695175cdd63ca32e0.webm?t=1770822592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/8f8db0bc275c751695175cdd63ca32e0.mp4?t=1770822592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《记忆卡牌》将卡牌制作游戏与一个令人回味的关于记忆消逝的故事融为一体。<br><br>玩家将扮演灯塔看守人 Joon，用一副珍藏回忆的手工卡片日记唤起回忆。<br><br>每段回忆都会在令人身临其境的全景透视板上进行卡牌对战。掌握战术牌组制作技巧，克服各种挑战，回忆每个细节。您每一回合的决策和深度定制的卡牌制作系统都能帮助您增强和完善自己独特的卡组。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/d5faf309ba6ac5d536ab7c3a0d953613.avif?t=1770822592\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras_big/d5faf309ba6ac5d536ab7c3a0d953613.avif?t=1770822592 width=800 height=102 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/0a1e64188ef20052550c794765373bd9.poster.avif?t=1770822592\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/0a1e64188ef20052550c794765373bd9.webm?t=1770822592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/0a1e64188ef20052550c794765373bd9.mp4?t=1770822592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在充满氛围的透视板上进行游戏，记忆会以卡牌的形式展现出来。在这款易上手难驾驭的卡牌对战游戏中，通过克服各种场景和随机事件，深入了解记忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/87717bf5c5a17a2ecdb43774e431ef38.avif?t=1770822592\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras_big/87717bf5c5a17a2ecdb43774e431ef38.avif?t=1770822592 width=800 height=102 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/5326882e4d33390d19d64d63b3eb176d.poster.avif?t=1770822592\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/5326882e4d33390d19d64d63b3eb176d.webm?t=1770822592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/5326882e4d33390d19d64d63b3eb176d.mp4?t=1770822592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >需要休息吗？在迷人的乡村灯塔中的壁炉边躲避一下吧。在制作台上摆弄你的卡牌，在个人相册中为你的收藏编目，并用定制的装饰来营造气氛。<br><br>随着游戏的深入，您将解锁新的卡牌碎片、制作工具和其他奇特的收藏品，为您的温馨小屋增添乐趣。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/ed0957170fb4fb41c8d5bf16a9e8230a.avif?t=1770822592\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras_big/ed0957170fb4fb41c8d5bf16a9e8230a.avif?t=1770822592 width=800 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/fe49cdd789a695ff99257416b0b1442e.poster.avif?t=1770822592\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/fe49cdd789a695ff99257416b0b1442e.webm?t=1770822592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/fe49cdd789a695ff99257416b0b1442e.mp4?t=1770822592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次游戏开始时，您都会获得一些基本卡牌，然后将它们制作成您独有的强大卡组。<br><br>每个回合，您都会收到随机的碎片，供您使用或插入卡牌，让您可以混合搭配各种能力和属性。提升卡牌等级，升级碎片池，从而影响您获得的碎片类型。发掘独特的碎片和被动能力，进一步定制您的玩法。掌握这些动态元素将考验你的战略技巧。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/49b4f462902ac4d8ba0bbde508453de0.avif?t=1770822592\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras_big/49b4f462902ac4d8ba0bbde508453de0.avif?t=1770822592 width=800 height=102 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/168c086414ad6c7529685a07bb0fec67.poster.avif?t=1770822592\" width=800 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/168c086414ad6c7529685a07bb0fec67.webm?t=1770822592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/168c086414ad6c7529685a07bb0fec67.mp4?t=1770822592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集并组合具有协同作用的卡牌碎片，完成突破性的组合。<br><br>制作系统拥有无与伦比的自由度和定制深度，让您完全掌控自己的卡牌和能力，支持无穷无尽的组合和策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/ca823020d8785ff1ac74e177536c6c0f.avif?t=1770822592\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras_big/ca823020d8785ff1ac74e177536c6c0f.avif?t=1770822592 width=800 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次游戏都与众不同。您可以选择和制作不同的卡牌，遭遇不同的敌人和怪物，探索多种可能的策略和卡片组合。<br><br>对于经验丰富的卡牌玩家来说，还能在更多高难度挑战中检验自己的技巧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/d44d4d904c8b0e70e2f21a893a168e03.webp?t=1770822592\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras_big/d44d4d904c8b0e70e2f21a893a168e03.avif?t=1770822592 width=800 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras/ad837953356731853f0706719c2c69db.avif?t=1770822592\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056570/extras_big/ad837953356731853f0706719c2c69db.avif?t=1770822592 width=800 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>仍在开发中：</strong>《记忆卡牌》目前正处于积极开发阶段 — 欢迎您参与！<br><br>加入我们的社区，试玩最新 Demo 并在 Discord 上分享您的反馈 — 我们非常期待见到您！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 德语, 法语, 意大利语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 简体中文, 日语, 韩语, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 俄语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 繁体中文<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
